Package: setools
Title: Swedish Registry Epidemiological Research Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-03-10
Authors@R: person("Timothy P", "Copeland", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "timothy.copeland@ki.se",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0000-0000"))
Description: R implementation of the Stata 'setools' package for Swedish
    registry-based epidemiological research. Provides tools for date parsing,
    migration registry processing, procedure code matching, Charlson Comorbidity
    Index computation (Swedish ICD adaptation), EDSS disability progression
    analysis (sustained, CDP, PIRA), and closest covariate extraction from
    longitudinal data. All functions use 'data.table' for performance.
